wn business using this template, <strong>download it now!</strong><span id="more-214188"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=213035&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-petshopper">Download</a> <a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/petshopper/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" alt="live" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214210" alt="petshop1" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop1.png" width="971" height="873" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">GENERAL SPECIFICATIONS</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214213" alt="petshop4" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop4.png" width="956" height="764" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">When you purchase one of our theme you can use our <strong>videotutorials</strong> to set the <strong>template</strong> and to customize it according to your <strong>business</strong> and <strong>marketing</strong> <strong>needs</strong>. It is easier with our videotutorials which you can watch to discover how to set each page of the theme step by step.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">If you’ve problems setting it due to some theme’s features, don’t worry! We provide <strong>free</strong> <strong>support</strong> for our themes: you can open a <strong>ticket</strong> on our support platform and ask help to our developers.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">PetShopper is a theme which is <strong>100%</strong> compatible with <strong>WPML</strong>. It has been <strong>projected</strong> with a great <strong>Responsive</strong> design and it is compatible with <strong>IE8+, Firefox, Chrome, Opera </strong>and<strong> Safari.</strong></p>\n<p>It is a WordPress theme, <strong>WP 3.2+ Compatible,</strong> it is Translation ready (.po and .mo files availables) and you can easily customize it. Indeed, it has Widget ready sidebars, Valid <strong>XHTML</strong> / <strong>CSS</strong> and a Blog structure which supports threaded comments.</p>\n<h2>STYLE</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214215" alt="petshop2" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop2.png" width="964" height="272" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can compose your<strong> front page</strong> choosing your <strong>favourite</strong> <strong>slider</strong> to display your product and service. You have <strong>3</strong> <strong>options</strong>: <strong>flexislider</strong>, <strong>elegant</strong> <strong>slider</strong> and <strong>thumbnail</strong> <strong>slider</strong>.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">To customize your website using PetShopper you can set <strong>custom</strong> <strong>widgets</strong> and you can choose your favorite <strong>portfolio</strong> <strong>layout</strong> to show and share your projects. Furthermore, you can use <strong>unlimited</strong> <strong>contact</strong> <strong>form</strong> for your site and set up each form very easily through our panel.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can choose your <strong>Fonts</strong> &amp; <strong>Colors</strong> to completely customize your website:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Over<strong> 600 Google fonts</strong> – google fonts list will be automatically updated;</li>\n<li>Set font and size for titles, slogan, body text and more;</li>\n<li>In the <strong>premium</strong> <strong>version</strong> of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links,slogan and so on.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>PRODUCTS PAGE</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214217" alt="petshop3" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop3.png" width="606" height="641" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">In the product’s page you can set the <strong>Wishlist</strong>, which gives to users the ability to add the <strong>products</strong> in their own withlist. Users can <strong>Compare</strong> <strong>products</strong> of your shop in one complete table.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can <strong>add</strong> <strong>more</strong> <strong>tabs</strong> in the <strong>product</strong> <strong>detail</strong> <strong>image</strong>, to add more features and informations about your products.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can add a <strong>zoom</strong> <strong>feature</strong> in the featured image of products, on the product detail page.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">With premium version you can have a new <strong>checkout</strong> <strong>layout</strong> with a <strong>multistep feature</strong> and you will have a way to choose the layout for the products list in the shop page; you can choose among <strong>grid</strong> and <strong>list</strong> <strong>view</strong>.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">In premium version you can add a <strong>popup</strong> to launch your <strong>offers</strong> and where the users can subscribe in your <strong>newsletter</strong> <strong>list</strong>. Furthermore, you can add an <strong>enquiry</strong> <strong>form</strong> inside each <strong>product</strong> <strong>detail</strong> <strong>page</strong> and you can add <strong>more</strong> <strong>tabs</strong> in the products tabs.</p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">SHORTCODE MANAGER WITH OVER 200 SHORTCODES</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214218" alt="petshop5" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop5.png" width="956" height="358" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">With our advanced theme options page, you are given complete control over your theme and its settings.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can use the <strong>Shortcode</strong> <strong>manager</strong> with <strong>200</strong>+ <strong>shordcodes</strong> ready to use, to add elements on each page with just one click, without copy and paste html/css code.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Typography</strong>: quote, columns, list styles, dropcap &amp; more</li>\n<li><strong>Elements</strong>: alert boxes, buttons, tables, toggles, tabs, price tables &amp; more</li>\n<li><strong>Media</strong>: sliders, galleries, videos, images styles, lightbox</li>\n<li><strong>Shop</strong>: product sliders, credit card icons and so on</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>SAMPLE DATA</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214219" alt="petshop6" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop6.png" width="984" height="938" /></p>\n<p>With a simple click you can import our <strong>demo</strong> <strong>files</strong>, so your theme will appear exactly like the theme preview.</p>\n<h2>CONCLUSIONS</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Would you like to have a responsive website with high quality design and which enables you to sell and show your products in a simple and easy to customize way?</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can choose PetShopper to achieve your goals in the web world.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Don’t you believe us?</strong></p>\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Donwload it now.</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=213035&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-petshopper">Download</a> <a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/petshopper/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" alt="live" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://yithemes.com/blog/free-themes/petshopper-e-commerce-theme-for-pets-products/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"12";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n	